                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860222-60-defend725 t17860222-60-punish331"></join>
               privately whipped and discharged
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. ROSE.</p>
